Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:24107,24983}Much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:24983,26693}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:29947,30948}The horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:45.58,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:42876,45587}Kitajima Maya, 13 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:45587,50676}An average girl-\Nnot too beautiful, not too smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:51176,53428}Auntie, hurry, hurry!\NThe next delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:01:01.47,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:54054,61478}But sleeping within her small and normal heart,\Nthere is a huge passion for acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.06,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:61478,63063}A ticket for the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.69,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63063,65691}You can have it if you want it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.86,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:65691,69861}But only if you promise to do\Nall the deliveries on New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:69861,72531}Delivery from Manpuku Ken.\NThanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.86,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:72531,75867}You have to do them all by midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:23.29,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:78996,83292}That means you'll have until the last ship\Nhas sounded its last horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:31.17,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:86169,91174}Tonight, all the ships that are stationed\Nin the Port of Yokohama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:33.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:91174,93677}will sound their horns\Nto welcome in the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99016,100809}Auntie, the next one.\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100809,102686}We have 120 deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102686,105314}It's impossible for you to do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:47.39,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105314,107399}I made such a ridiculous promise because\NI knew she wouldn't be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:50.27,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107399,110277}That ticket is for Matsumoto,\Nand I will be going with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121496,123582}I'll get that ticket no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126543,127669}Sugiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127669,129755}What are you putting a coat on for?\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129755,132215}Yamashita Park.\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134301,136094}Two ramens.\NHere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136094,137095}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137679,139556}I'm running out of time.\NI have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141642,144936}I have to hurry.\NI have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182933,185936}Oh no… Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185936,189439}It was impossible from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189439,191733}What a silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199408,200367}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200367,201660}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202202,205247}I got them all done before 12,\Njust as I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205247,206748}Sugiko… Where's Sugiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209418,210585}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210585,212838}I finished them all, just like I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217050,219010}Give me the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219010,222389}F-Fine, if you want it that bad,\Nyou can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222389,223348}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223348,225517}What's so important about this anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225517,227394}Here!\NGo get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234526,235485}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241241,242159}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244578,246580}I can go!\NI can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246580,248874}I can go to the play with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249374,250917}That girl is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250917,251960}She really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253962,255920}Finally, I've found her.
