Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405742,409451}Excuse me, miss, the play is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409451,411912}Sorry, miss…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411912,414748}Everyone has left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424549,425425}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.92,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:425008,427928}Ondine Theatre\NStudents wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430180,432015}"Students wanted".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432015,433350}Ondine Theatre…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461753,462629}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464965,467592}What a big place!\NI feel a bit overwhelmed…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473723,475725}Thank you very much, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475725,478144}II will be leaving early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478144,479354}That's Ms. Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479354,480188}How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480188,481856}She doesn't look 13 years old at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:08.98,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:483024,488989}Himekawa Ayumi, the daughter of\Na renowned movie director and a famous actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.49,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:488989,491491}With beautiful looks\Nand a talent for acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.03,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:491491,494035}she is steadily progressing\Nalong the road to stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495120,497998}She's the same age as I am?\NI can't believe it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507465,512012}Excuse me, I saw the advertisement\Nand I would like to apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512012,513847}You want to be a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513847,515724}Fill this out, and take the exam, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515724,517308}Exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517308,521229}The admission fee and the tuition\Nwill only be paid after you pass the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521229,523523}Admission fee and tuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523523,526943}The admission fee is ¥150.000,\Nand the tuition will be ¥20.000 per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526943,532323}Six months' tuition has to be paid in advance,\Nso the total will be ¥270.000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:56.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532323,536119}¥270.000… there's no way I\Ncan come up with that much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538872,540040}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544044,546254}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546254,548254}…you are not concentrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552802,557263}No, no!\NThis is pantomime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558308,560101}Panto… mime?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562145,564981}Ayumi, can you show them how it's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564981,568443}How about doing the "Escaped Bird"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568443,569694}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:41.12,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:576576,581122}Onodera Hajime, a well-known producer\Nwho serves as the director of the Ondine Theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:45.21,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:581122,585210}as well as a member\Nof the Japanese Drama Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625458,628211}Wow!\NIt's as if she's actually summoned a bird on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647272,648565}It landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648565,651651}I can actually see the bird perched on her finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671796,673089}Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689063,689981}Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721054,722722}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722722,724098}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724098,725266}Oh, you're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727810,729938}That's not good…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729938,731439}Get ready to administer first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731439,732941}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732941,735026}No, I'm fine! I can walk.\NReally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735026,737320}Please, let me go.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:28.16,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:743993,748164}Sakurakōji Yū, a student at Ondine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:32.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:748164,752710}Despite only being a high school student,\Nhe is already expected to become a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:37.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:753586,757423}Hayami Masumi, the young president\Nof Metropolitan Entertainment,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:757423,759676}the sponsor company of Ondine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:44.18,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:759676,764180}With his cool looks he is known as\Nthe "King of Work" in the industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765056,766474}Oh, there's blood on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766474,767267}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775191,776651}Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776651,778361}It looks just like a purple flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807307,810351}I want to act…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810351,812729}Oh no, I'll get scolded again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813938,816649}I told them I'd get home early, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.53,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:820069,822530}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821154,823239}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823239,825616}Hurry up and get changed\Nso you can lend us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825616,826826}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830747,831831}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831831,833124}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833124,837462}Look at you!\NYou can't do one thing right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837462,841883}You're only able to attend school\Nbecause they let me work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841883,843883}{\an8}Yes, yes, it'll be just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842925,846387}If you keep pulling stunts like this,\Nhow am I going to manage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847347,849057}I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849057,852310}Maya, it's okay,\Ncan you go deliver now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852310,853102}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853102,856606}This person paid ¥10.000\Nfor a bowl of ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856606,857940}¥10.000?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857940,862320}It's a little far up the hill,\Nbut could you take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878669,879712}Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904153,905488}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906989,908574}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908574,910034}I'm from Manpuku Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915623,917540}I'm here with your ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919544,921337}Hello…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928845,931097}Anyone… home…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949699,950865}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956205,957623}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957623,959417}A script for Princess Camellia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962462,964589}Do you like that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970344,973514}O-Oh yes, I've seen this play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973514,974515}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974515,976809}So if I asked, you could recite the story to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976809,978811}Yes, but I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985818,987904}The curtain silently rises,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987904,992867}and the first scene starts\Nwith a gorgeous dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992867,999999}A young man, Alfred, sets his eyes\Nupon a beautiful woman with a camellia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999999,1001542}"How beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001542,1002960}"Who is she?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002960,1005129}"You don't know her?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005129,1007340}– "She's a diva called Princess Camellia."\N– My apologies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007340,1010009}but Mr. Masumi from Metropolitan Entertainment\Nis here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010009,1011761}Have him wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011761,1014013}I'll wait 'til you are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017099,1020645}She's difficult as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020645,1025650}But we have to play her way\N'til we get the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025650,1030821}We must get the rights to that dramatic masterpiece,\N"The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030821,1032365}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032365,1035117}It was 32 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035117,1039205}Miss Tsukikage's "Crimson Goddess"\Nwas truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039205,1040957}It was a massive hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040957,1043000}Ozaki Ichiren, the playwright,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043000,1048005}claimed that only Tsukikage Chigusa\Ncould possibly play the main role,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048005,1052468}and gave her all the rights to the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052468,1057098}My father still desperately craves those rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057098,1058349}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058349,1060768}"When can I see you next?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062103,1064897}"When this camellia has withered."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064897,1069110}"I will be with you\Nif I wear a white camellia,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069110,1071904}but I will refuse you if the camellia is red."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071904,1073739}No, no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073739,1077076}The tone of the voice,\Neye movement, spacing, nothing is good—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077076,1078244}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080663,1082123}Mr. Onodera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082123,1086669}She has only seen "Princess Camellia" once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086669,1087670}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087670,1095386}But she memorized the entire 3-hour script\Nwithout a single mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112361,1113738}That rude woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119619,1122747}I am confident we will find a way\Nto get those play rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128210,1131756}If Metropolitan Entertainment wishes it,\Nthen it will be made possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141682,1143559}I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143559,1145227}I want to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147980,1153944}I'm not pretty or smart,\Nand I can't afford drama school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153944,1155863}I'm not even that well proportioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155863,1159116}But… But…\NI want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165373,1169752}If it costs money, I can work,\Nbut I want to act!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169752,1175007}Drama is much more difficult than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177385,1181639}If this is just a half-hearted passion,\Nthen you should forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181639,1183641}My passion isn't half-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183641,1187311}I will do anything to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187311,1188229}Are you sincere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188229,1189188}I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190606,1193109}I would like to show you something, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193109,1194527}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209792,1211627}We have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213754,1215131}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.59,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1217383,1220594}Tsukikage Theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220761,1221762}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232440,1234442}This is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234442,1238195}I was once an actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238195,1240823}but I suffered a cruel twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248706,1250750}It has been twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250750,1253794}This is my drama research center.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253794,1257173}I have awaited this day for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257173,1261135}Today I am finally ready\Nto open Tsukikage Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273773,1276692}Please let me join you!\NI want to be part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279612,1282448}Being an actress\Nis not a hobby or a pastime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286577,1290790}Why do you want to be part\Nof Tsukikage Theatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290790,1292750}What are you going to do after you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292750,1294418}I'll be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296587,1299256}I want to be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322321,1323906}Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323906,1325825}Those are the words I\Nwanted so desperately to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347513,1348472}That girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:40.86,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1353269,1360860}13-year-old Maya had no idea\Nwhat grand and difficult future awaited her.{NOTE:行く手に渦巻く陰謀のドラマが待ち受けているとも知らない My an 13歳の春だった}
Comment: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:48.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1368367,1368367}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:23:01.63,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1375583,1381630}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:07.67,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1381630,1387678}{\blur3}and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:19.77,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1387678,1399773}{\blur3}Something calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:31.91,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1399773,1411911}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:37.75,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1411911,1417750}{\blur3}more sure than words,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:43.92,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1417750,1423923}{\blur3}telling us gently
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:50.01,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1423923,1430012}{\blur3}that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:56.01,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1430012,1436018}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:02.06,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1436018,1442066}{\blur3}for the dream\Non my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:08.07,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1442066,1448072}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}belongs to you.
