Comment: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:18.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1458457,1458457}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:25.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1461001,1465673}Maya gets chosen to play Beth,\Nthe lead role in "Little Women",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:27.96,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1465673,1467967}the first play at Tsukikage Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.96,0:24:34.01,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1467967,1474014}Despite suffering from a 40-degree fever,\Nshe stands upon the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.01,0:24:38.18,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1474014,1478185}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Mr. Purple Rose".
